Class SqmEnumLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.sqm.tree.expression.SqmEnumLiteral
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Expression<Enum>, Selection<Enum>, TupleElement<Enum>, JpaCriteriaNode, JpaExpression<Enum>, JpaSelection<Enum>, JpaTupleElement<Enum>, SemanticPathPart, SqmExpressable<Enum>, SqmExpression<Enum>, SqmSelectableNode<Enum>, SqmNode, SqmTypedNode<Enum>, SqmVisitableNode

    public class SqmEnumLiteral
extends Object
implements SqmExpression<Enum>, SqmExpressable<Enum>, SemanticPathPart
    Specialized SQM literal defined by an enum reference. E.g. ".. where p.sex = Sex.MALE"
